  "description": "Obsidian / Obsidian Publish.",
  "body_html": "<p>There are countless of blog posts that praise <a href=\"https://obsidian.md/\">obsidian</a>. After trying Notion, my notepad, emacs and others, I think obsidian really does take the cake as the most - intuitive, useful and feature-laden<em> app I\u2019ve used so far. </em></p><p>It\u2019s hard to find tools that make note-taking actually fun, but this comes pretty close. </p><p><a href=\"http://casualphysicsenjoyer.com\">I\u2019\u2019ve also made a website to go with this blog</a>!</p><p>I\u2019m experimenting with <em>Obsidian publish to do this</em>. It lets me easily publish my obsidian notes. It covers the bases where Substack lacks - namely writing structured  / wiki-like content, writing equations, and just general integration with custom tools that I\u2019ve built. </p><p>Check it out!</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FlQY!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2130e8b-8ebf-4c5c-ab56-ef7d1f8022f2_2806x1410.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FlQY!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2130e8b-8ebf-4c5c-ab56-ef7d1f8022f2_2806x1410.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FlQY!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2130e8b-8ebf-4c5c-ab56-ef7d1f8022f2_2806x1410.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FlQY!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2130e8b-8ebf-4c5c-ab56-ef7d1f8022f2_2806x1410.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!FlQY!,w